{"tid":1204631,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"唔敢衝既你應該聽朝應該買機票出走散心","createTime":"2019-06-11T15:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T16:25:45.000Z","uid":44663,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1dbf0272beaa0698fb30886c6293f53bfa4f5955","tid":1204631,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:40:42.000Z","msg":"平時除左樓價股票，地鐵一死就最多人討論<br />\n全港市民都知地鐵車唔多，一架又放唔到好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時返工時間半分一架都迫爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲下立法後會唔會屌港鐵都俾人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以聽朝都係突然想去旅行離開多事之地<br />\nBtw我每次都帶2個30吋gip去搭地鐵去機場<br />\n雖然幾阻地方，咁我真係需要嘛<br />\n<br />\n同時又好驚咁趕出發會唔會有事delay<br />\n你知啦返工時間好易有人訓到總站唔知醒<br />\n一個唔覺意司機睇唔到調頭果陣先拉手掣仲delay得耐<br />\n<br />\n唉，拎住2個30吋gip都係唔帶八達通<br />\n用散紙買飛算<br />\n當然我都係會著全黑支持大家<br />\n<br />\n呀！ 呢排轉天好多人病都係帶埋口罩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d98dbfd2bd6b3105fb1a7058ed0a541dc88accc9","tid":1204631,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:43:37.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"115474783c83698cabb8999e65852470e7b63ecc","tid":1204631,"uid":44663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:25:45.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}